00:00:25,283 --> 00:00:26,571
Yes, Dr Crane.

7
00:00:26,572 --> 00:00:29,231
On line four, we have Russell from Kirkland

8
00:00:30,212 --> 00:00:33,772
Hello, Russell. This is Dr. Frasier Crane; I'm listening

